text: "Tip Toe" is a 2017 song by American singer Jason Derulo featuring Moroccan- American rapper French Montana. It went to number 5 in the United Kingdom, number 11 in Germany, number 12 in Ireland, number 18 in Finland, number 19 in Belgium, number 22 in Switzerland, number 25 in Austria, number 35 in Hungary and number 50 in Canada. == Track listing == * Digital download # "Tip Toe" (featuring French Montana) â€“ 3:07 == References == Category:2017 songs Category:Jason Derulo songs
